Exercise:
Set the border to "2px solid green" for table, th and td elements.

Answer: table {
  border-collapse: collapse;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
table {
  border-collapse: collapse;
}
table, td, th {
  border: 1px solid black;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Firstname</th>
    <th>Lastname</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Peter</td>
    <td>Griffin</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>Lois</td>
    <td>Griffin</td>
  </tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
